title: Selected Works: Poems
creator: Voltairine de Cleyre
description: LibriVox recording of selected pems, by Voltairine de Cleyre. Voltairine de Cleyre (November 17, 1866 – June 20, 1912) was an American anarchist. She was skilled in many subjects and wrote essays, poems, letters, sketches, stories and speeches. These are her selected poems.
